@startuml 5C_Moderation_Defaults
title 5-C · Comment Moderation Workflow (UC-F17, UC-T14)

start
|Registered Fan|
:Open published blog post;
:Write a comment;

|System|
:Require logged-in fan\n(include UC-F02 Login if needed);
if (Fan authenticated?) then (No)
  :Redirect to login;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Validate comment body and tenant scope;
endif

if (Comment valid?) then (No)
  :Return 422 validation error;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Create BlogComment record;
  :Display comment if not hidden;
endif

|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
:Open Blog > Comments;
:Review reported or inappropriate comments;
if (Moderation action?) then (Hide)
  |System|
  :Set BlogComment.is_hidden = true;
  :Remove comment from public listings;
  :Preserve original record for audit;
elseif (Moderation action?) then (Restore)
  |System|
  :Set BlogComment.is_hidden = false;
  :Show comment again;
else (Delete)
  |System|
  :Reject deletion;\ncomments are hidden, not hard-deleted;
endif

|System|
:Return updated comment status to admin UI;
stop
@enduml
